        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Boston</placeName>
                <date>Dec 20 1862</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> Â Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">We are in receipt of<lb/> a letter from <persName>Mr Moses
                    Piza</persName>
                <placeName>St. Thomas<lb/> W I</placeName> enclosing second of draft on us<lb/> in
                your favor at 10 D/S amount<lb/> forty seven &amp; 78/100 Dollars ($47.78).
                Please<lb/> endorse <hi rend="underline">the enclosed</hi> and send to us<lb/> by
                mail or by private hands if you<lb/> prefer and we will on presentation<lb/> pay it
                not taking the 10 days time.<lb/> If you should send to us by mail<lb/> we will send
                you check on <placeName>Philad</placeName><lb/> by return of mail.</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">Yours very respy</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <persName role="author">W F Hasken &amp; Co</persName>
            </p>
            <p>Please write us in regard the above<lb/> in order to Record where we may find
                the<lb/> draft as we wish it paid at once.</p>
        </body>
